Laboratory 09: SPI Transmitter and Receiver
Objective: Functionality of the SPI master has a DORD input  added. This input selects whether the serial byte is transmitted most significant bit first or least significant bit first. A MISO input is also added. This input receives serial data sent from the slave to the master. The byte received is output at data_out.

Task 1: Data Order Selection and Receiver Enable
Task 2: SPI Receive Shifter
Task 3: SPI Test System II Top Level